'''罗伯特·穆德'''（Robert Mood，1958年12月8日－ ）是一名[[挪威|挪威]][[少将|少将]]，是[[联合国停战监督机构|联合国停战监督机构]]的负责人<ref name=Reuters>{{Cite news |title= Cool Nordic head faces uphill task as Syria U.N. monitor |author= Koranyi, Balazs; Apps, Peter; Charbonneau, Louis; Nichols, Michelle; Scrutton, Alistair; Elgood, Giles; Allen, Vicki |url= http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/27/us-syria-mood-idUSBRE83Q0KN20120427 |publisher= [[Reuters|Reuters]] |date= 27 April 2012 |accessdate= 27 April 2012}}</ref>。2012年他担任[[联合国叙利亚监督团|联合国叙利亚监督团]]团长。

==个人生活==
他生于挪威[[泰勒马克郡|泰勒马克郡]]的海岸小镇[[克拉格勒|克拉格勒]]。他家人是19世纪来自[[瑞典|瑞典]]的移民<ref name=VL>{{Cite news |title= Veteranenes general |trans_title= The veterans' general |author= Blystad, Stig-Øyvind |newspaper= [[Vårt_Land_(Norwegian_newspaper)|Vårt Land]] |language= Norwegian |page= 26 |date= 10 October 2011}}</ref>。他有一个姐姐和一个妹妹<ref name=Reuters/>。他的家人经常从事[[航海|航海]]、[[打猎|打猎]]、[[爬山|爬山]]等自然活动<ref name=VL/>。他从小就梦想在退休以后能在一艘古老的[[帆船|帆船]]上自由生活<ref name=NRK/>。

他的妻子是Eva Tverberg，一位来自[[卑爾根|卑爾根]]的[[法学家|法学家]]与官员<ref>{{Cite news |title= Nye jurister tok eksamen i Bergen |trans_title= New jurists graduated in Bergen |newspaper= [[Aftenposten|Aftenposten]] |language= Norwegian |page= 10 (morning edition) |date= 5 October 1992}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= Oslo-folk klager mye mer enn før |trans_title= Oslo people complain more than before |author= Trine, Dahl; Ingvild, Gjerstad |newspaper= Aftenposten |language= Norwegian |page= 7 (evening edition, news section) |date= 25 January 2001}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= NORDMENN I BRUSSEL Byråkrater jobber gratis for EU 12 år gammel ordning - ...sikrer EU billig arbeidskraft Skaffer kompetanse til nytte for Norge. |trans_title= NORWEGIAN IN BRUSSELS Bureaucrats work for free for EU 12 year old arrangement - ...securing EU cheap labour Obtaining skills useful for Norway. |author= Ask, Alf Ole|newspaper= Aftenposten |language= Norwegian |page= 16 (morning edition, section "Innsikt") |date= 31 May 2006}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= Departementsnei til ja takk-merker |trans_title= Ministry no to yes stickers |author= Guttormsen, Irene Hegge |newspaper= [[Agderposten|Agderposten]] |language= Norwegian |page= |date= 12 September 2009}}</ref>，两人育有一个儿子（2009年5月7日出生）<ref>{{Cite news |title= Født |trans_title= Born |newspaper= Aftenposten |language= Norwegian |page= 12 (morning edition, section Navn, part 2) |date= 12 May 2009}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= Babyfoto mandag |trans_title= Baby photo Monday |newspaper= [[Bergens_Tidende|Bergens Tidende]] |language= Norwegian |page= B005 |date= 25 May 2009}}</ref><ref name=Reuters/>。

他毕业于军事学院，并具备了一些[[外交|外交]]技能，为人风趣机智<ref name=Reuters/>。

他不认为自己是个[[基督徒|基督徒]]，更自认为是个[[人本主义|人本主义]]者<ref>{{Cite news |title= Kan denne mannen sikre fred i Midtøsten? |trans_title= Can this man secure peace in the Middle East? |author= Winge, Åge; Nordahl, Aleksander (photographer) |newspaper= [[Dagens_Næringsliv|Dagens Næringsliv]] |language= Norwegian |page= 47 |date= 10 January 2009 |quote= - Jeg betrakter meg mer på den humanistiske tradisjonen, enn det å beskrive meg som personlig kristen. Jeg tror på noe som er større enn menneskene, men hva det er har jeg vanskelig for å definere.}}</ref>。

在接受[[挪威广播公司|NRK]]采访时他表示，他将[[歌剧|歌剧]]比喻为自己的工作，“ 一部好的歌剧总是能够可以融化各种困难的元素，最终让人印象深刻。”<ref name=NRK>{{Cite news |title= Ban Ki-moon har utpekt Robert Mood til observatørsjef  |trans_title= Ban Ki-moon has appointed Robert Mood to chief of observers |author= Aanensen, Kristian; Tvegård, Anders |url= http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/verden/1.8100428 |publisher= [[Norwegian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Norwegian Broadcasting Corporation]] |language= Norwegian |date= 25 April 2012 |accessdate= 27 April 2012}}</ref><ref name=Reuters/>

